  "body": "### Primary button - All over the app (hover state broken)\r\n**Current**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"600\" alt=\"Screen_Shot_2021-01-22_at_18_05_38\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105521691-83e02f00-5cdc-11eb-833b-c4a30ff57ec7.png\">\r\n<img width=\"560\" alt=\"Screen_Shot_2021-01-22_at_18_06_31\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105521758-9ce8e000-5cdc-11eb-9a5b-cddad6fc9742.png\">\r\n\r\n+ ALL OVER THE APP, MOSTLY IN SETTINGS + WALLET?\r\n\r\n**Fix**\r\nBehaviour\r\n<img width=\"260\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 18 08 13\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105521877-cc97e800-5cdc-11eb-9dfc-a4a3c461d788.png\">\r\n\r\n **Hover State Color: FF2D55 20% Opacity**\r\n \r\n\r\n### Status updates button (active state &Â hover state broken, font weight is wrong)\r\n\r\n#### Current\r\n<img width=\"248\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 16 12\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105517643-97d56200-5cd7-11eb-86a7-d52c7cc41b86.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Fix\r\n**Active State**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"204\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 30 15\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105517683-a3c12400-5cd7-11eb-97b8-5cf331db88e3.png\">\r\n\r\n**Hover State**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"212\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 30 17\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105517694-a7ed4180-5cd7-11eb-841f-8ae16e7260d2.png\">\r\n\r\nFont weight: 400\r\n\r\nFigma here:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/n0NB83EpT076bc1xQBKdYg/%F0%9F%97%A3-Status-Updates%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=1927%3A0\r\n\r\n### Reset notification settings button (active state &Â hover state broken) + wrong positioning \r\n\r\n#### Current\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105518300-690bbb80-5cd8-11eb-9f3f-9c42d89a7870.mov\r\n<img width=\"423\" alt=\"Screen_Shot_2021-01-22_at_17_38_10\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105518543-b5ef9200-5cd8-11eb-9724-8b72e733a23b.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Fix\r\n**Active State**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"637\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 37 17\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105518349-7a54c800-5cd8-11eb-88e4-547122a03071.png\">\r\n\r\n**Hover State**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"991\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 37 51\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105518408-8e98c500-5cd8-11eb-98d2-616088049fbd.png\">\r\n\r\nFont weight: 400\r\n\r\nFigma here:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/Zz6KMBxwrB0l2NPgsjnPjq/%F0%9F%91%A4-Profile%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=1559%3A72\r\n\r\n### Block User + More red buttons all over the app (hover state broken)\r\n\r\n#### Current\r\n\r\n<img width=\"444\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 55 14\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105520426-fe0fb400-5cda-11eb-81cf-662ab731f129.png\">\r\n\r\n #### Fix\r\n **Hover State Color: FF2D55 20% Opacity**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"388\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 49 18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105519810-277c1000-5cda-11eb-97d3-2489246898a9.png\">\r\n\r\nFigma here:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/BTS422M9AkvWjfRrXED3WC/%F0%9F%91%8B-Onboarding%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=590%3A298\r\n\r\n### Back & Forward buttons in modals (No hover state)\r\n#### Current\r\n<img width=\"670\" alt=\"Screen_Shot_2021-01-22_at_17_50_20\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105520000-67db8e00-5cda-11eb-9b5c-55450500fd0b.png\">\r\n<img width=\"608\" alt=\"Screen_Shot_2021-01-22_at_17_42_39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105520029-72962300-5cda-11eb-92bc-95df8a44d774.png\">\r\n\r\n####Fix\r\n\r\n**Hover color: 4360DF 20% Opacity**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"386\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-22 at 17 52 38\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105520165-9eb1a400-5cda-11eb-95b0-68e5b2d29d1d.png\">\r\n\r\nFigma here:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/BTS422M9AkvWjfRrXED3WC/%F0%9F%91%8B-Onboarding%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=590%3A298\r\n",
